 set this image as the post\'s Featured Image.'=>'选中此选项来设置这张图片作为文章的特色图片。','Select one or more image metadata field to be displayed along with the image upload field. They enable users to enter additional information about the uploaded image.'=>'选择一个或多个图像元数据字段与图像上传字段一起显示。他们允许用户输入有关上传图像的附加信息。','Image Meta'=>'图像元数据','Selecting this option will set the post author to the WordPress user that submitted the form.'=>'选择这个选项将设置文章作者为提交的表单的WordPress用户。','Use Current User as Author'=>'用当前用户作为作者','Select the category that will be used for the post that is created by the form entry.'=>'选择将用于通过表单条目输入创建的文章分类。','Check this option to format and insert merge tags into the Post Title.'=>'选中此选项去格式化和插入合并标签到文章标题。','Post Title Template'=>'文章标题模版','Check this option to format and insert merge tags into the Post Content.'=>'检查该选项去格式化和合并标签插入到文章内容。','Post Content Template'=>'文章内容模板','Select the post format that will be used for the post that is created by the form entry.'=>'选择将用于表单条目输入而创建的文章格式。','Select the author that will be used for the post that is created by the form entry.'=>'选择将用于表单条目输入而创建的文章作者。','Post Author'=>'文章作者','Select the post status that will be used for the post that is created by the form entry.'=>'选择将用于表单条目输入而创建的文章状态。','Select which categories are displayed. You can choose to display all of them or select individual ones.'=>'选择显示哪些分类。您可以选择显示所有的或个别选择。','Create rules to dynamically display or hide the submit button based on values from another field.'=>'创建规则来动态显示或隐藏基于另一个字段值的提交按钮。','Create rules to dynamically display or hide the page\'s Next Button based on values from another field.'=>'创建规则来动态显示或隐藏该页面上的基于另一个字段值的下一步按钮。','Next Button Conditional Logic'=>'下一步 按钮条件逻辑','Enter the path to an image you would like to use as the page previous button.'=>'输入您想用于页面的上一步按钮的一个图像的路径。','Previous Button Image'=>'选择图像的大小','Enter the text you would like to appear on the page previous button.'=>'输入您想在页面上一步按钮上显示的文本。','Previous Button Text'=>'后退按钮文本','Enter the path to an image you would like to use as the page next button.'=>'输入您想用于页面的下一步按钮的一个图像的路径。','Next Button Image'=>'下一步按钮图片','Enter the text you would like to appear on the page next button.'=>'输入您想在下一步按钮上显示的文本。','Next Button Text'=>'前进按钮文本','Name each of the pages on your form.  Page names are displayed with the selected progress indicator.'=>'在您的表单上的每个页面的名字。页面名称随着选定的进度指示器显示。','Select which progress bar style you would like to use.  Select custom to choose your own text and background color.'=>'选择您想使用的进度条样式。选择“自定义”来选择您自己的“文本”和“背景颜色”。','Select which type of visual progress indicator you would like to display.  Progress Bar, Steps or None.'=>'选择要显示的视觉进度指示器类型。进度条，步骤或无。','Create rules to dynamically display or hide this page based on values from another field.'=>'创建基于另一个字段值动态显示或隐藏这个页面的规则。','Page Conditional Logic'=>'页面条件逻辑','Enter a message to be displayed to users who are not logged in (shortcodes and HTML are supported).'=>'输入显示给未登录用户的信息（简码和HTML的支持）。','Check this option to require a user to be logged in to view this form.'=>'勾选这个选项以要求用户登录后查看这个表单。','Check this option to add a text input as the final choice of your radio button field. This allows the user to specify a value that is not a predefined choice.'=>'请检查此选项以添加一个文本输入作为您的单选按钮字段的最后选择。这允许用户指定一个值，它不是一个预定义的选择。','"Other" Choice'=>'“其他”选择','Enable Enhanced UI'=>'启用增强的用户界面','Create rules to dynamically display or hide this field based on values from another field.'=>'创建基础另一个字段的值来动态地显示或隐藏这个字段的规则。','Check this option to specify a value for each choice. Choice values are not displayed to the user viewing the form, but are accessible to administrators when viewing the entry.'=>'选中此选项为每个选择指定一个值。选择不显示给用户查看表单的值，但在查看该条目时，可访问管理员。','Enable Choice Values'=>'启用选择值','Field Choices'=>'字段选择','Enter the CSS class name you would like to use in order to override the default styles for this field.'=>'输入您想使用的CSS类名称以覆盖这个字段的默认样式。','Select the language you would like to use for the reCAPTCHA display from the available options.'=>'选择您想使用的reCAPTCHA可用选项显示的语言。','reCAPTCHA Language'=>'reCAPTCHA 语言','If you would like to override the default error validation for a field, enter it here.  This message will be displayed if there is an error with this field when the user submits the form.'=>'如果您想重写一个字段的默认错误验证，在这里输入它。当用户提交表单时，如果有一个错误，该消息将被显示。','Validation Message'=>'验证消息','Select this setting to display the option as activated by default when the form first loads.'=>'选择此设置，当表单第一次加载时默认激活以显示选项。','Activated by Default'=>'默认激活','Select the field to be used as the source for the values for this field.'=>'选择该字段作为这个字段值的来源','Enter the label to be displayed next to the check box. For example, &quot;same as shipping address&quot;.'=>'输入要在复选框旁边显示的标签。例如，&quot;送货地址&quot;。','Activate this option to allow users to skip this field and submit the values entered in the associated field. For example, this is useful for shipping and billing address fields.'=>'激活这个选项允许用户跳过这个字段，然后提交相关字段中输入的值。例如，这是用于送货和结算的地址字段。','Use Values Submitted in a Different Field'=>'在一个不同字段中提交使用的值','Placeholders will not be submitted along with the form. Use Placeholders to give a hint at the expected value or format.'=>'占位符将不会随着表单提交。使用占位符在预期的值或格式上获得一个提示。','The Placeholder will not be submitted along with the form. Use the Placeholder to give a hint at the expected value or format.'=>'占位符将不会随着表单提交。使用占位符在预期的值或格式上获得一个提示。','If you would like to pre-populate the value of a field, enter it here.'=>'如果您想预先填充一个字段的值，在这里输入它。','Select the fields you\'d like to use in this Address Field and customize the Sub-Labels by entering new ones.'=>'选择您想在该地址栏中使用的字段，并通过输入新的子标签来定制子标签。','Add Choices to this field. You can mark a choice as selected by default by using the radio buttons on the left.'=>'添加选择到这个字段。您可以在默认情况下，通过选择单选按钮左边使用默认的选择。','Name Prefix Choices'=>'选择名称前缀','Select the fields you\'d like to use in this Name field and customize the Sub-Labels by entering new ones.'=>'选择您想这个名称字段中使用的字段，然后通过输入新的标签来定制子标签。','Select a form field size from the available options. This will set the width of the field. Please note: if using a paragraph field, the size applies only to the height of the field.'=>'在可用选项中设置表单字段的尺寸。这将设置字段的宽度。请注意：文本字段的尺寸只有高度不同。','Select the sub-label placement.  Sub-labels can be placed above the field inputs or below the field inputs.'=>'选择子标签放置。子标签可以放在字段输入的上面或字段输入的下面。','Select the description placement.  Descriptions can be placed above the field inputs or below the field inputs.'=>'选择描述位置。描述可以放置在输入字段上面或输入字段的下面。','Select the label visibility for this field.  Labels can either inherit the form setting or be hidden.'=>'选择该字段的标签可见性。标签可以继承的表单设置或隐藏。','Label Visibility'=>'标签的可见性','Enter values in this setting to override the Sub-Label for each field.'=>'在这个设置中输入值来重写每个字段的子标签。','Enter the admin label of the form field.  Entering a value in this field will override the Field Label when displayed in the Gravity Forms administration tool.'=>'输入表单字段的管理标签。在这个字段中输入一个值将覆盖在Gravity表单管理工具中显示的字段标签。','Admin Label'=>'管理标签','Specify how many decimal places the number should be rounded to.'=>'指定小数点后多少位数应四舍五入。','Specify a mathematical formula. The result of this formula will be dynamically populated as the value for this field.'=>'指定一个数学公式。这个公式的结果将作为这个字段值的动态填充。','Enabling calculations will allow the value of this field to be dynamically calculated based on a mathematical formula.'=>'启用计算将使这个字段的值是基于一个数学公式动态计算的。','Enter the minimum and maximum values for this form field.  This will require that the value entered by the user must fall within this range.'=>'输入该表单字段的最小和最大值。这将要求用户输入的值必须在该范围内。','Number Range'=>'数量范围','Select this option to limit user input to unique values only.  This will require that a value entered in a field does not currently exist in the entry database for that field.'=>'选择这个选项来限制用户输入惟一值。这将要求在字段中输入的值不存在于该字段的输入数据库中。','Select this option to make the form field required.  A required field will prevent the form from being submitted if it is not filled out or selected.'=>'选择这个选项我作为该表单要求的字段。一个要求的字段将防止表单被提交时不填写或选择。','Required Field'=>'必填项目','Enter the description for the form field.  This will be displayed to the user and provide some direction on how the field should be filled out or selected.'=>'输入表单字段的描述。这将显示给用户，并提供在这个字段应该如何填写或选择一些方向。','Field Description'=>'字段描述','Select the format you would like to use for the phone input.  Available options are domestic US/CANADA style phone number and international long format phone number.'=>'选择您想使用的电话输入格式。可用的选项是国内美国/加拿大国际长格式风格的电话号码和电话号码。','Phone Number Format'=>'电话号码格式','Specify the maximum file size in megabytes allowed for each of the files.'=>'指定允许的每个文件的最大文件大小，以兆字节为单位的。','Specify the maximum number of files that can be uploaded using this field. Leave blank for unlimited. Note that the actual number of files permitted may be limited by this server\'s specifications and configuration.'=>'指定文件可以上传使用的最大数量。留空为无限。注意，文件允许的实际数量可能会受到该服务器的规格和配置。','Select this option to enable multiple files to be uploaded for this field.'=>'选择这个选项，使这个字段可以上传多个文件。','Enter the allowed file extensions for file uploads.  This will limit the type of files a user may upload.'=>'输入允许文件上传的文件扩展名。这将会限制用户可以上传文件的类型。','Allowed File Extensions'=>'允许文件扩展名','Select the format you would like to use for the time field.  Available options are 12 hour (i.e. 8:30 pm) and 24 hour (i.e. 20:30).'=>'选择您想使用的时间字段格式。可用的选项是 12小时(如 8:30 pm)和 24小时(如20:30)。','Select the format you would like to use for the date input.'=>'选择要用于输入日期的格式。','Field Date Format'=>'字段日期格式','Check this box to prevent this field from being displayed in a non-secure page (i.e. not https://). It will redirect the page to the same URL, but starting with https:// instead. This option requires a properly configured SSL certificate.'=>'勾选此项，防止这个字段显示在一个不安全的页面上(例如：非https://)。它将重定向页面相同的UR，但从 https:// 开头。这个选项需要正确配置SSL证书。','Select the format of numbers that are allowed in this field. You have the option to use a comma or a dot as the decimal separator.'=>'允许选择数字的格式。您可以选择使用一个逗号或一个点作为小数分隔符。','Select the format you would like to use for the Name field.  There are 3 options, Normal which includes First and Last Name, Extended which adds Prefix and Suffix, or Simple which is a single input field.'=>'选择您想使用的名字字段格式。有三个选项，其中包名字和姓氏，扩展了前缀和后缀，或者说是一个简单的输入字段。','Field Name Format'=>'名称（要求）：','Check this box to prevent the State/Province/Region from being displayed in the form.'=>'勾选此项，防止州/省/地区显示在表单中。','Hide State/Province/Region'=>'隐藏州/省/地区','Check this box to prevent Province field from being displayed in the form.'=>'勾选此项，阻止省字段被显示在表单中','Hide Province Field'=>'隐藏省份字段','Check this box to prevent the State field from being displayed in the form.'=>'勾选此项，阻止州字段被显示在表单中','Hide State Field'=>'隐藏州字段','Check this box to prevent the extra address input (Address Line 2) from being displayed in the form.'=>'勾选此项，防止额外的地址输入(地址行2)被显示在表单中。','Hide Address Line 2'=>'隐藏地址行2','For addresses that only apply to one country, you can choose to not display the country drop down. Entries will still be recorded with the selected country.'=>'对于仅适用于一个国家的地址，您可以选择不显示下拉菜单。条目仍将记录与所选择的国家。','Hide Country'=>'隐藏国家','Select the country you would like to be selected by default when the form gets displayed.'=>'选择您想要默认选中时显示的国家。','Select the province you would like to be selected by default when the form gets displayed.'=>'选择您想要默认选中时显示的省份。','Default Province'=>'默认省份','Select the state you would like to be selected by default when the form gets displayed.'=>'选择您想要的默认选中时显示状态。','Default State'=>'默认州','Select the type of address you would like to use.'=>'选择您想要使用的地址类型。','Select the type of inputs you would like to use for the date field. Date Picker will let users select a date from a calendar. Date Field will let users free type the date.'=>'选择要使用的日期字段的输入类型。日期选择器可以让用户从日历中选择日期。日期字段将让用户自由输入的日期。','Enter the maximum number of rows that users are allowed to add.'=>'输入允许用户添加的最大行数。','Enter the maximum number of characters that this field is allowed to have.'=>'输入这个字段是允许的最大字符数。','Select the type of field from the available form fields.'=>'从可用的表单字段选择字段类型。','Field type'=>'字段类型','Select the custom field name from available existing custom fields, or enter a new custom field name.'=>'从现有自定义字段中选择自定义字段名称，或输入一个新的自定义字段名。','Select the type of CAPTCHA you would like to use.'=>'选择您想使用的验证码类型。','CAPTCHA Type'=>'验证码类型','Select the visual theme for the reCAPTCHA field from the available options to better match your site design.'=>'选择用于reCAPTCHA字段的视觉主题，以更好的匹配您的网站设计。','reCAPTCHA Theme'=>'reCAPTCHA 主题','When enabled, margins are added to properly align the HTML content with other form fields.'=>'当启用时，边距被添加到适当与其他表单字段的HTML内容对齐。','Disable Default Margins'=>'禁用默认边距','Enter the label for this HTML block. It will help you identify your HTML blocks in the form editor, but it will not be displayed on the form.'=>'输入该HTML块标签。它将帮助您识别您的HTML块的表单编辑器，但它不会显示在表单中。','Enter the label of the form field.  This is the field title the user will see when filling out the form.'=>'输入表单字段的标签。这是外面用户在填写表单时会看到的标题。','Pass Data Via Query String'=>'通过查询字符串传递数据','Enter the URL of the webpage you would like the user to be redirected to after they have submitted the form.'=>'输入您希望用户提交表单后被重定向到的网页的URL。','Redirect Form to URL'=>'重定向URL形式','Select the page you would like the user to be redirected to after they have submitted the form.'=>'选择您希望用户在提交表单后重新被重定向到页面。','Redirect Form to Page'=>'重定向表单到页面','When enabled, auto-formatting will insert paragraph breaks automatically. Disable auto-formatting when using HTML to create the confirmation content.'=>'启用时，自动格式化将插入段落自动中断。禁用，自动格式化时使用HTML创建确认内容。','Enter the text you would like the user to see on the confirmation page of this form.'=>'输入您希望用户在这个表单的确认页面上看到的文本。','Confirmation Message Text'=>'确认信息文本','Enter the URL of a custom image to replace the default \'delete item\' icon. A maximum size of 16px by 16px is recommended'=>'输入自定义“删除选项”的按钮图片链接。图片的最大尺寸是16*16px。','Enter the URL of a custom image to replace the default \'add item\' icon. A maximum size of 16px by 16px is recommended'=>'输入自定义“添加选项”的按钮图片链接。图片的最大尺寸是16*16px。','Enter the CSS class name you would like to use in order to override the default styles for this form.'=>'输入要用以覆盖这个表单默认样式CSS的类名称。','Form CSS Class Name'=>'表单的CSS类名','Enter the path to an image you would like to use as the form submit button.'=>'输入您想使用在表单提交按钮上的一个图像的路径。','Form Button Image'=>'表单按钮图像','Enter the text you would like to appear on the form submit button.'=>'输入您想在表单提交按钮上显示的文本。','Form Button Text'=>'表单按钮文本','Select the default sub-label placement.  Sub-labels can be placed above the field inputs or below the field inputs. This setting can be overridden in the appearance settings for each field.'=>'选择默认的子标签放置。子标签可以放在字段输入的上面或字段输入的下面。这个设置可以为每个字段被设置外观。','Select the default description placement.  Descriptions can be placed above the field inputs or below the field inputs. This setting can be overridden in the appearance settings for each field.'=>'选择默认的描述位置。描述可以放置在该字段输入的上面或该字段输入的下面。这个设置可以为每个字段设置外观。','Form Label Placement'=>'表单标签位置','Enter a description for your form. This may be used for user instructions.'=>'输入您的表单的说明。这可用于用户指令。','Enter the title of your form.'=>'输入您的表单的标题。','Check this option to enable a sliding animation when displaying/hiding conditional logic fields.'=>'选中此选项，在显示/隐藏条件逻辑字段时启用滑动动画。','Enable Animation'=>'启用动画','Schedule a time period the form is active.'=>'安排一个时间周期内活跃的表单。','Enter a number in the input box below to limit the number of entries allowed for this form. The form will become inactive when that number is reached.'=>'在下面的输入框中输入一个数字来限制允许这个表单条目的数量。当表单达到这个数字时将变为非活跃，。','Limit Number of Entries'=>'限制条目数量','Limit the number of entries a form can generate and/or schedule a time period the form is active.'=>'限制条目的数量可以生成一种形式和/或安排一个时间段是活跃的。','Limit Form Activity'=>'限制表单行为','Enter a comma separated list of email addresses you would like to receive a BCC of the notification email.'=>'输入一个逗号用分隔的你想收到秘密抄送通知邮件的电子邮件地址列表。','Blind Carbon Copy Addresses'=>'密件抄送地址','Enter the email address you would like to be used as the reply to address for the notification email.'=>'输入你想被用作电子邮件地址的电子邮件地址。','Enter the name you would like the notification email sent from, or select the name from available name fields.'=>'输入你想发送的通知邮件名称，或选择可用的名称字段的名称。','From Email Address'=>'从电子邮件地址','Allows notification to be sent to different email addresses depending on values selected in the form.'=>'允许将根据在表单中选择的值发送通知到不同的电子邮件地址。','Routing'=>'路由','When enabled, auto-formatting will insert paragraph breaks automatically. Disable auto-formatting when using HTML to create email notification content.'=>'当启用时，自动格式化将自动插入换行符。禁用，自动格式化时使用HTML创建电子邮件通知内容。','Disable Auto-Formatting'=>'禁用自动格式化','Enter the email address you would like the notification email sent to.'=>'输入发送的通知邮件的电子邮件地址。','Send To Email Address'=>'发送到电子邮件地址','New submission from'=>'新的提交表单','User Login'=>'用户登入','User Email'=>'用户邮箱','User Display Name'=>'显示用户姓名','HTTP Referer URL'=>'HTTP 引用 URL','HTTP User Agent'=>'HTTP用户代理','Embed Post/Page Title'=>'嵌入文章/页面标题','Embed Post/Page Id'=>'嵌入文章/页面 ID','User IP Address'=>'用户 IP 地址','Insert Merge Tag'=>'插入MergeTag','Pricing Fields'=>'价格字段','Post Fields'=>'文章字段','The form title you have entered is already taken. Please enter a unique form title.'=>'您输入的表单标题已存在。请输入一个独特的表格标题。','Enable Next Button Conditional Logic'=>'启用下一个按钮条件逻辑','Enable Page Conditional Logic'=>'启用页面条件逻辑','Enable Conditional Logic'=>'开启逻辑条件','Allow field to be populated dynamically'=>'允许现场进行动态填充','Use the Rich Text Editor'=>'使用富文本编辑器','Visibility'=>'能见度','Force SSL'=>'强制SSL','Enable Password Input'=>'启用密码输入','Delete Icon URL'=>'删除URL图标','Add Icon URL'=>'添加URL图标','Zulu'=>'祖鲁','Vietnamese'=>'越南语','Urdu'=>'乌尔都语','Ukrainian'=>'乌克兰','Turkish'=>'土耳其语','Thai'=>'泰语','Telugu'=>'泰卢固语','Tamil'=>'泰米尔语','Swedish'=>'瑞典语','Swahili'=>'斯瓦希里语','Spanish (Latin America)'=>'西班牙语 （拉丁美洲）','Spanish'=>'西班牙语','Slovenian'=>'斯洛维尼亚语','Slovak'=>'斯洛伐克语','Serbian'=>'塞尔维亚','Russian'=>'俄语','Romanian'=>'罗马尼亚列语','Portuguese (Portugal)'=>'葡萄牙语(葡萄牙)','Portuguese (Brazil)'=>'葡萄牙语(巴西)','Portuguese'=>'葡萄牙语','Polish'=>'波兰语','Persian'=>'波斯','Norwegian'=>'挪威语','Marathi'=>'马拉地语','Malayalam'=>'马拉雅拉姆语','Malay'=>'马来西